&lt;P&gt;Around Planes of Power and Lost Dungeons of Norrath, you could see it in hard numbers.&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Which expansion launched almost 75000 new EQ accounts?&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;If you answered Planes of Power, you'd be wrong. Lost Dungeons of Norrath signed up more new players by an order of magnitude than Planes of Power (a lot of those 'new' players were cancelled players who started playing again. I was in a guild at the time that had close to 20 people come back to EQ because of LDON. They quit because of Planes of Power).&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Lost Dungeons of Norrath didn't cater to the people who usually are asking for more content, it catered to what most people PLAY.&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Hassan al-Nasir&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
