&lt;HR&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/BLOCKQUOTE&gt;&lt;BR&gt;LDoN brought two new things to the table that reeled in subscriptions. Augments and Instancing. Greater enhancement of gear and playing without dealing with 30-60 other people bogging you down and irritating you worked wonders. Now you have people crying for classic servers and less instancing. Weird. I bet most of the Devs pretend they're Willy Wonka on their off time, isolating themselves from all human contact. Cause people are weird, unexpected and weird.</description>
