ng break and at 55 the game is awful. Groups are scarce, and because of that the xp is so slow that I am thinking of leaving. That is not because I want to but because it is taking forever to &amp;quot;get to the game&amp;quot;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If anything they need to speed up the exp grind to 65 by twofold, then let those who chose to, delay as they see fit rather then shackle the rest of us for months while we try to get to the game.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
